<text id="02-output-contract" title="domain-driven-design Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema (draft-07) for the code artefact this methodology produces, with valid and invalid examples and forbidden patterns.</summary>

  <section title="Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/domain-driven-design.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": [
    "bounded_context",
    "aggregate_roots",
    "value_objects",
    "ubiquitous_language_count",
    "framework_imports_in_domain"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "bounded_context": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 2
    },
    "aggregate_roots": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "value_objects": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "string"
      }
    },
    "ubiquitous_language_count": {
      "type": "integer",
      "minimum": 5
    },
    "framework_imports_in_domain": {
      "const": 0
    },
    "context_map_path": {
      "type": "string"
    }
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "bounded_context": "ordering",
  "aggregate_roots": [
    "Order",
    "Customer"
  ],
  "value_objects": [
    "Money",
    "Address"
  ],
  "ubiquitous_language_count": 18,
  "framework_imports_in_domain": 0,
  "context_map_path": "docs/context-map.md"
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "bounded_context": "x",
  "aggregate_roots": [],
  "value_objects": [],
  "ubiquitous_language_count": 1,
  "framework_imports_in_domain": 4
}
]]></code>
    <note>Bounded context name too short; no aggregate roots; framework imports leaked into domain; ubiquitous language too thin.</note>
  </example>

  <section title="Forbidden">
    <forbidden id="f1">Domain logic in services / controllers / handlers.</forbidden>
    <forbidden id="f2">Framework imports inside the domain layer.</forbidden>
    <forbidden id="f3">Implicit bounded-context boundaries (no context map document).</forbidden>
    <forbidden id="f4">Mutable value objects.</forbidden>
  </section>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-domain-driven-design.py">Validator script.</reference>
</text>
